metadata.name: FuDaoVerse VIP DAO Pass #1
metadata.description: These 888 VIP DAO members will form the core team of our DAO and will represent the overall community and voices of FuDaoVerse. VIP DAO members are entitled to free mints on our future collections in support of Chinese culture. 1 Pass = 4 Free Mints on Our Collection + Future Whitelists
